Text:
What a frustrating download.  The two "seeders" have themselves so throttled that I've been stuck at 99.9% for hours now. 

Rest assured that if I *ever* get to 100% that I AM THE ONE sharing this video.  Everyone else who gets 100% as a result has a moral obligation to continue my good work!!!!!

My download is complete and I am seeding.  The vid looks very good- Eddie & The Cruisers, the first movie, not the sequel. 

I'll seed this for a while, courtesy of my high bandwidth, but the rest of you MUST continue sharing it after that. 

Like our parents taught us early on, it's nice to share.

Almost 24 hours later I continue to seed, and while I note that some have finished their download and then disconnected, others continue to seed.  Good for you! 

This file looks and sounds great- it's well worth downloading and well worth sharing.
Thanks for the up ....  Do You have EDDIE LIVES ....Eddie And The Cruisers 2 ????  I've seen it but would like to add it to my collection
I will keep seeding this for a few days. It's now 2008, so if anyone is paying attention, I'll be seeding.
Maybe I will seed. Now that I hit the download link, there are no people on here seeding it. So, unless I get a chance to DL it, I will not be seeding.
Wow, I guess this movie isn't as popular as I thought lol  I will help this movie live on. It's an excellent movie with some great music.
